name: Wonders of the World
description:
"The world is filled with greatness & wonder.
Magnificence & glory.
Flawless beauty across the entire universe,
With love, understanding, patience & truth we co-exist,
With time we evolve & become even better.
This is our world:
Beautiful, simple & fully natural.
The world we all chose to begin,
a place like no other"
